-- Manziel, Klein, Te’o Shortlisted for Football’s Heisman Trophy
-- B y   D e x   M c L u s k e y
-- 2012-12-03T23:46:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-12-03/manziel-klein-te-o-shortlisted-for-football-s-heisman-trophy.html
Texas A&M quarterback Johnny Manziel,
his Kansas State counterpart Collin Klein and Notre Dame
linebacker Manti Te’o were shortlised for the Heisman Trophy,
awarded annually to college football’s best player.  Nicknamed “Johnny Football,” Manziel is the favorite
to become the first freshman to win the accolade, according to
online sportsbook Bovada.lv.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dex McLuskey at 
 dmcluskey@bloomberg.net  